Today she is ready to teach you how to cook mouth-watering empanadas in the shortest possible time. In this fun free online cooking game for girls, your role is to prepare a scrumptious Empanadas Dough by just following her instructions properly. 

You are sure to have great fun while cooking some tummy-tastic spicy empanadas with some special teacher Sara Cooking Class. You will definitely try preparing your home once you play this popular flash game in your browser. This highly challenging and interesting free online game is designed for girls of all ages. Apart from helping you learn the delicious empanadas shortly, Empanadas Sara Cooking Class game will also allow you to make the most fun out of the online cooking game. 

You should definitely try playing this fun new game ? Sara Cooking Class Empanadas if you are pretty excited to learn some new cooking recipe. Following Sara instructions properly will be enough to cook such a mouth-watering recipe of the Mexican cuisine ? the empanadas. You have to prepare this recipe within a time frame in this cool flash game. Play this game now and prepare empanadas in future to surprise your friends and family. Join Sara Cooking Class to learn another lesson from her. Remember, the faster you prepare, the more bonus points you will be able to earn. All the best!
